edBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T13:56:56.000Z","msg":"執柒咗支支tvb慳返頻譜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:34:01.000Z","msg":"加埋港台33"},{"pid":"0eb7d81f2c43bfcf6560ebce03c88c36e82a38e2","tid":2399936,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:40:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ofca.gov.hk/filemanager/ofca/tc/content_92/majortasks_19-20_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ofca.gov.hk%2Ffilemanager%2Fofca%2Ftc%2Fcontent_92%2Fmajortasks_19-20_c.pdf&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUiso9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=f6b43dd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ofca.gov.hk/filemanager/ofca/tc/content_92/majortasks_19-20_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n16. 考慮到數碼地面電視用戶滲透率和覆蓋情況，以及香港<br />\n在實現數碼紅利方面的安排，政府於二零一九年二月十一日公布將<br />\n於二零二零年十一月三十日起終止模擬電視服務（終止模擬廣播）。<br />\n政府亦計劃於終止模擬廣播後，在600／700兆赫頻帶內騰空合共<br />\n160兆赫的頻譜作流動服務之用。我們會繼續與內地當局就終止模擬<br />\n廣播後協調470 &ndash; 806兆赫頻帶頻譜的使用事宜，<span class=\"red\">並會協調相關的電<br />\n視廣播機構遷移其數碼地面電視頻道，藉以騰空600／700兆赫頻帶<br />\n內的頻譜</span>。我們亦會向商經局提供技術支援，以落實終止模擬廣播<br />\n的安排。"},{"pid":"6247d103ce9e1b0318c6f91bd12125973d2b525a","tid":2399936,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-09T06:20:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bcc1e2c60e4e4132cb513bd889b7a8700467ae2","tid":2399936,"uid":329544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0eb7d81f2c43bfcf6560ebce03c88c36e82a38e2","tid":2399936,"uid":5889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T14:40:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.ofca.gov.hk/filemanager/ofca/tc/content_92/majortasks_19-20_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww